s improvement. We will show you how this business improvement methodology, encompassing intense activity over a short period, typically 1 – 4 weeks, can bring about significant improvements in the business process(es). We will teach you how to deliver this improvement process in 8-steps.","topics":["The Process of Rapid Business Improvement - Learning Outcomes","Fundamentals of Rapid Business Improvement","Delivering Rapid Business Improvement Part – 1","Delivering Rapid Business Improvement Part – 2","The Process of Rapid Business Improvement - Lesson Summary"]},{"name":"Module","details":"Course assessment","description":"","topics":["Course assessment"]}],"slides":["\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"3info\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h4><b>Learning Outcomes</b></h4></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"DD4Ne\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list paragraph, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"editable p-asset ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\">Having completed this course, you will be able to: </div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"H5IHs\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Define rapid business improvement.</li><li class=\"\">Discuss the fundamentals o